                    <lb n="2" break="no"/>ṇi Aruḷā niṉṟa <hi rend="grantha">śāli</hi>-vā<supplied reason="omitted"><hi rend="grantha">ha</hi></supplied>ṉa <hi rend="grantha">śakāb</hi>ta<hi rend="grantha">m</hi> 1508 ṉ mēl cellā niṉṟa viya samvaṟsarattu Āṣāṭa nāyaṟṟu pūṟuva pakṣattu yintu vā śaramum
