                    <lb n="11" break="no"/>saṉam Āka paṇṇi kuṭuttōm Inta Āyirattu Aññūṟu kuṭikkum varum <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> ṣepa-jala-pāṣāṇa-kṣaṇa Akādi vari tēsācata ṭṭaṉaka
